STATE EX REL. REICHLEY
v.
INDUS. COMM. 2017-0883 Supreme Court of Ohio. March 1, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MEDIATION MATTERS

Case returned to the regular docket under S.Ct.Prac.R. 19.01. Appellant shall file a brief within 40 days, and the parties shall otherwise proceed in accordance with S.Ct.Prac.R. 16.02 through 16.07. As provided in S.Ct.Prac.R. 16.07, the court may dismiss this case or take other action if the parties fail to timely file merit briefs.
